Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: ​​​​​​​District at 6th is a brand new luxury apartment community carefully crafted in clean and contemporary modern architecture. The community is comprised of 213 units in two four-story elevator-served buildings that include an underground parking structure with 216 spaces. The community offers an exclusive set of amenities including a swimming pool with sundeck, dog park, gas grills and fire pit, and a fully equipped fitness center. This premier asset is located in the Historic East Village, downtown Des Moines’ most desirable neighborhood. With convenient access to I-235, District at 6th offers easy access to the Greater Des Moines area. The East Village is a rapidly evolving “live-work-play” neighborhood featuring a vibrant and constantly growing based of dining, entertainment, shopping and nightlife options, allowing residents to experience a truly urban lifestyle.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: CBRE|Hubbell Commercial is pleased to offer for sale Verve & Velocity, a 243-unit best-in-class multifamily portfolio strategically located in downtown Des Moines’ historic East Village neighborhood- one of the metro’s most desirable neighborhood featuring an eclectic mix of area attractions, boutique shopping, award-winning restaurants, and nightlife.

Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: The Ankeny market has maintained very strong and consistent rental occupancies as there has been large population growth and there is an overwhelming demand for rental housing, especially at affordable price points. The existing rental rates are significantly below market, which will provide an investor the opportunity to increase rents without spending significant capital on improvements leading to immediate upside potential. Additional value add potential exists through implementing a RUBS billback system (common to area), consistently charging pet rent/fees, late fees, increasing laundry income, and short term/month-to-month fees. Additionally, opportunities exist to generate more income by building garages in the excess land, and completing the renovations of the remaining 32 units.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: CBRE|Hubbell Commercial is the exclusive advisor for the multifamily sale of Ankeny Pine Apartments located at 1713, 1717, 1801, 1805, 1809 NW Pine Road in Ankeny, Iowa. This 52-unit rental development was constructed in 1975. The community has been well-maintained. This apartment community features 32 one-bedroom/one-bathroom units and 20 two-bedroom/one-bathroom units, ranging in size from 675 square feet to 850 square feet. Equipped with private balconies/patios, full appliance packages, some with modern upgrades, and a true community setting, nestled in the heart of Ankeny.  The tenant  base at Ankeny Pine is stable and strong, and many are long-term renters. The property boasts many major upgrades, including 20 remodeled units.

CBRE|Hubbell Commercial is pleased to offer for sale, Arlington Heights Apartments, a 36-unit value-add apartment community just two miles north of downtown Des Moines in the historic River Bend Neighborhood. Arlington Heights is just off the 6th Avenue corridor that is undergoing significant revitalization.
